口述实录 | 我40多天没去过重点地区，为何要隔离？他们说：因为你的身份证是武汉的！。
I haven't been to a key district in more than 40 days, so why isolate me? They say: Because your ID card is Wuhan!
赵先生、黄祺。
Mr. Zhao and Mr. Huang Qi.
